Package: spacedecorr
Type: Package
Title: Spatial De-correlation for Single-Cell Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Gabriela", "Vasconcelos",
           email = "anagabipv@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fits gene-wise generalized additive models with spatial smoothers
    to remove spatially induced correlations and adjust for covariates in
    single-cell spatial data, returning decorrelated residuals for downstream
    analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
